UID:2Poz9_29cWDMYA9d58yHw
SUMMARY:Keep Bellevue Beautiful - West Side Cleanup
DTSTAMP:20260406T013628Z
DTSTART:20260411T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Keep Bellevue Beautiful - West Side Cleanup\n\nEReed\n\nTue\, 0
	3/10/2026 - 16:17\n\nApril 11 2026\n\n9:00 AM - 11:00 AM\n\nAll Day Event\
	n\nOff\n\nEvent Registration\n\nFree\n\nContact\n\nEvan Reed\n\nEmail\n\ne
	reed@bellevuewa.gov\n\nTelephone\n\n425-452-5372\n\nLocation\n\nCity Hall\
	, 450 110th Ave NE\n\nDescription\n\nThe City of Bellevue's Keep Bellevue 
	Beautiful program is launching\n\n26 in '26\,\n\nan effort aimed at comple
	ting\n\n26 Signature Street cleanups\n\nin 2026. The goal is simple: show 
	up consistently\, take care of our streets and support cleaner\, more welc
	oming neighborhoods.\n\nDate:\n\nSaturday\, April 11\n\nTime:\n\n9-11 a.m.
	\n\nStart Location:\n\nBellevue City Hall\n\nFor this special West Side Cl
	eanup\, volunteers will begin at City Hall before choosing their own clean
	up route across any of the following neighborhoods:\n\nBridle Trails\n\nNo
	rthwest Bellevue\n\nBelRed\n\nDowntown\n\nWilburton\n\nWoodridge\n\nWest B
	ellevue\n\nFactoria\n\nNewport\n\nExperience is not required\, and all cle
	anup supplies will be provided. Volunteers are welcome to stay for the ful
	l two hours or drop in and help for as long as they can. Coffee and water 
	will be available.\n\nWhen you're done\, simply leave your filled trash ba
	gs and gear at the previously agreed upon location within your cleanup nei
	ghborhood. A staff member will retrieve everything at the end of the event
	.\n\nRegister:\n\nCleanWestBellevue.EventBrite.com\n\nHide from City Calen
	dar\n\nOff\n\nCanceled\n\nOff\n\nLocation\n\nCity Hall\n\nhttps://seatoday
	.6amcity.com/events/#/details/keep-bellevue-beautiful-west-side-cleanup/18
	493268/2026-04-11T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/keep-bellevue-beautiful-w
	est-side-cleanup/18493268/2026-04-11T00
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
