UID:pkzaiZ9gpSuqppO60Pzix
SUMMARY:HAPPY HOUR
DTSTAMP:20260406T013629Z
DTSTART:20260416T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description FREE Event for Lynnwood Chamber Members & their Gue
	sts - please register in advance. JANUARY HAPPY HOUR What better way to st
	art the New Year than being in the presence of fitness\, & healthy lifesty
	le options?? Join us Wednesday\, January 29th at STRETCHLAB LYNNWOOD from 
	5:30 pm to 7:30 pm\, where you'll get to mingle & network with other Chamb
	er Members in an environment known for reducing stress\, muscle & joint pa
	in\, improving posture & flexibility\, and increasing our range of motion!
	 This is event is FREE to all Chamber Members & their Guests\, who registe
	r in advance! We're the Lynnwood Chamber of Commerce & we mean business...
	and networking!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/happy-hou
