BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tmsR9zHeNMkaSj0pb2amU
SUMMARY:CROSSROADS BELLEVUE INVITES COMMUNITY TO  ‘LIVE MUSIC AT THE MARKET
	 STAGE
DTSTAMP:20260406T013630Z
DTSTART:20260419T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Crossroads Bellevue\, a one-of-a-kind shopping\, dining\, and e
	ntertainment destination in the heart of Bellevue\, Washington \\(https://
	crossroadsbellevue.com\\)\, invites the community to enjoy “Live Music at 
	the Market Stage\,” a series of free live musical performances held in the
	 public market every Friday \\(7 p.m. to 8:45 p.m.\\)\, Saturday \\(7 p.m.
	 to 8:45 p.m.\\)\, and Sunday \\(12:30 p.m. to 2:30 p.m.\\) now through th
	e end of the year. Performances include an eclectic mix of acoustic guitar
	\, Cuban music\, jazz\, local choirs and more. All performances are free o
	f charge. To learn more about each upcoming performance\, visit Market Sta
	ge | Crossroads Bellevue. While enjoying the music\, guests are encouraged
	 to dine at one of the center’s many restaurants. For more information abo
	ut Crossroads Bellevue\, visit https://crossroadsbellevue.com.\n\nhttps://
	seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/crossroads-bellevue-invites-communit
	y-to-live-music-at-the-market-stage/18468806/2026-04-19T00\n\nFrom SEAtoda
	y - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/crossroads-bellevue-invit
	es-community-to-live-music-at-the-market-stage/18468806/2026-04-19T00
LOCATION:CROSSROADS BELLEVUE\, 15600 NE 8th Street\, Bellevue\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:n3Bwicxz19_KcHSOasxW9
SUMMARY:O-Jak Watch Party
DTSTAMP:20260406T013630Z
DTSTART:20260419T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:O-Jak Watch Party is a community gathering hosted by the O-Jak 
	Bridge Art & Dance Festival\, an annual Seattle performing arts festival f
	eaturing artists from diverse cultural and artistic backgrounds. Enjoy net
	working\, food\, a live dance performance\, and a screening of last year’s
	 festival—plus the first reveal of the upcoming 2026 festival theme.\n\nRS
	VP Required: https://partiful.com/e/PzdyRvxfLdFEh3HKYYcJ?c=Ufqt0rhc\n\nhtt
	ps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/o-jak-watch-party/18305788/2026
	-04-19T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/o-jak-watch-party/1830578
	8/2026-04-19T00
LOCATION:Central Cinema\, 1411 21st Ave\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:saGQQzx8JQq1SwHDqU_Pa
SUMMARY:Scout Day at the Garden for Younger Scouts
DTSTAMP:20260406T013630Z
DTSTART:20260419T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come and work on scout badges and achievement requirements at t
	he Botanical Garden! Designed for K-3rd grade Girl Scouts and Cub Scouts\,
	 Scouts will visit stations in the Education Center and go on a nature wal
	k. Some of the topics include: composting with worms\, insects\, Leave No 
	Trace\, planting seeds\, and pollination. Scouts will receive a garden fun
	 patch and a list of completed activities towards their badges or achievem
	ents. \n\nTo make the check-in process smoother\, we are asking 2nd and 3r
	d graders to come at 12:20 pm at the earliest\, and K-1st graders to come 
	at 12:45 pm.  If you have a mix of ages\, anytime between 12:30 and 12:45 
	is fine.  You can leave when you are done. Adult chaperones are free.  Ema
	il Us with any questions or to register a group. \n\n$12 per scout.\n\nhtt
	ps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/scout-day-at-the-garden-for-you
	nger-scouts/18185400/2026-04-19T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/scout-day-at-the-garden-f
	or-younger-scouts/18185400/2026-04-19T00
LOCATION:Bellevue Botanical Garden\, 12001 Main St\, Bellevue\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H30M
END:VEVENT
